name: $certain
desc: This record is a close match, but not a certain match. Additional review (e.g. by a human) may be required before using this as a match.

name: $probable
desc: This record may be a matching one. Additional review (e.g. by a human) SHOULD be performed before using this as a match.

name: $possible
desc: This record is known not to be a match. Note that usually non-matching records are not returned, but in some cases records previously or likely considered as a match may specifically be negated by the matching engine.
